name: Vessels 193 :Space Cowboy 375
description: There was once a  cowboy who lay dying in the street.  He asked a passing stranger to give his love to a lady named Rose.  The stranger decided he would go one better and uploaded the cowboy's consciousness to a mechanical wonder.  Now he walks among the citizens of the colony with a gun on his hip and hat on his shiny robot head.  All hail the Space Cowboy.
